rateLimitTable.name: rateLimitTable
rateLimitTable.description: High-level (non-sampled) data about an action set with a rate limit.

rateLimitEntry.name: rateLimitEntry
rateLimitEntry.description: An entry in the rate limit list. Rows cannot be created or deleted.

rateLimitGlobalID.name: rateLimitGlobalID
rateLimitGlobalID.description: The global identifier of an action set with a rate limit.

rateLimitRequestedRate.name: rateLimitRequestedRate
rateLimitRequestedRate.description: The bit rate (in Kbps) set requested by the action set creator.

rateLimitActualRate.name: rateLimitActualRate
rateLimitActualRate.description: The bit rate (in Kbps) set up at the hardware level.

rateLimitPacketsSent.name: rateLimitPacketsSent
rateLimitPacketsSent.description: The number of packets sent via this rate limiter since last cleared.

rateLimitPacketsDropped.name: rateLimitPacketsDropped
rateLimitPacketsDropped.description: The number of packets dropped by this rate limiter since last cleared.

rateLimitPacketsQueued.name: rateLimitPacketsQueued
rateLimitPacketsQueued.description: The number of packets queued up to be sent via this rate limiter.

rateLimitHistNumSeconds.name: rateLimitHistNumSeconds
rateLimitHistNumSeconds.description: The number of seconds of valid historical (sampled) data available.

rateLimitHistNumMinutes.name: rateLimitHistNumMinutes
rateLimitHistNumMinutes.description: The number of minutes of valid historical (sampled) data available.

rateLimitHistNumHours.name: rateLimitHistNumHours
rateLimitHistNumHours.description: The number of hours of valid historical (sampled) data available.

rateLimitHistSecondsTable.name: rateLimitHistSecondsTable
rateLimitHistSecondsTable.description: Historical (sampled) data every second for a minute.

rateLimitHistSecondsEntry.name: rateLimitHistSecondsEntry
rateLimitHistSecondsEntry.description: An entry in the rate limit history seconds table. Rows cannot be created or deleted.

rateLimitHistSecondsGlobalID.name: rateLimitHistSecondsGlobalID
rateLimitHistSecondsGlobalID.description: The global identifier of an action set with a rate limit.

rateLimitHistSecondsBytesSent.name: rateLimitHistSecondsBytesSent
rateLimitHistSecondsBytesSent.description: The number of bytes sent via this rate limiter in the specified second.

rateLimitHistSecondsTimestamp.name: rateLimitHistSecondsTimestamp
rateLimitHistSecondsTimestamp.description: The time SecondsBytesSent was updated (in seconds since January 1, 1970).

rateLimitHistMinutesTable.name: rateLimitHistMinutesTable
rateLimitHistMinutesTable.description: Historical (sampled) data every minute for an hour.

rateLimitHistMinutesEntry.name: rateLimitHistMinutesEntry
rateLimitHistMinutesEntry.description: An entry in the rate limit history minutes table. Rows cannot be created or deleted.

rateLimitHistMinutesGlobalID.name: rateLimitHistMinutesGlobalID
rateLimitHistMinutesGlobalID.description: The global identifier of an action set with a rate limit.

rateLimitHistMinutesBytesSent.name: rateLimitHistMinutesBytesSent
rateLimitHistMinutesBytesSent.description: The number of bytes sent via this rate limiter in the specified minute.

rateLimitHistMinutesTimestamp.name: rateLimitHistMinutesTimestamp
rateLimitHistMinutesTimestamp.description: The time MinutesBytesSent was updated (in seconds since January 1, 1970).

rateLimitHistHoursTable.name: rateLimitHistHoursTable
rateLimitHistHoursTable.description: Historical (sampled) data every hour for a day.

rateLimitHistHoursEntry.name: rateLimitHistHoursEntry
rateLimitHistHoursEntry.description: An entry in the rate limit history hours table. Rows cannot be created or deleted.

rateLimitHistHoursGlobalID.name: rateLimitHistHoursGlobalID
rateLimitHistHoursGlobalID.description: The global identifier of an action set with a rate limit.

rateLimitHistHoursBytesSent.name: rateLimitHistHoursBytesSent
rateLimitHistHoursBytesSent.description: The number of bytes sent via this rate limiter in the specified hour.

ThresholdFilterState.name: ThresholdFilterState
ThresholdFilterState.description: The state of a threshold filter: red if the major threshold has been crossed, yellow if the minor threshold has been crossed, green if OK.

thresholdTable.name: thresholdTable
thresholdTable.description: High-level (non-sampled) data about a traffic threshold filter.

thresholdEntry.name: thresholdEntry
thresholdEntry.description: An entry in the traffic threshold filter list. Rows cannot be created or deleted.

thresholdGlobalID.name: thresholdGlobalID
thresholdGlobalID.description: The global identifier of a traffic threshold filter policy group.

thresholdState.name: thresholdState
thresholdState.description: The state (green, yellow, red) of this traffic threshold filter.

thresholdUnits.name: thresholdUnits
thresholdUnits.description: The units value (e.g., packets/sec) monitored by this threshold filter.

thresholdHistSecondsGlobalID.description: The global identifier of a traffic threshold filter.

thresholdHistSecondsUnitCount.name: thresholdHistSecondsUnitCount
thresholdHistSecondsUnitCount.description: The count of filter-specific units matching the traffic criteria for this filter in the specified second.

thresholdHistSecondsTimestamp.name: thresholdHistSecondsTimestamp
thresholdHistSecondsTimestamp.description: The time SecondsUnitCount was updated (in seconds since January 1, 1970).

thresholdHistMinutesTimestamp.name: thresholdHistMinutesTimestamp

tptThresholdNotifyDeviceID.name: tptThresholdNotifyDeviceID
tptThresholdNotifyDeviceID.description: The unique identifier of the device sending this notification.

tptThresholdNotifyPolicyID.name: tptThresholdNotifyPolicyID
tptThresholdNotifyPolicyID.description: The unique identifier of the policy causing this notification.

tptThresholdNotifySignatureID.description: The unique identifier of the signature associated with the policy.

tptThresholdNotifySegmentName.name: tptThresholdNotifySegmentName
tptThresholdNotifySegmentName.description: A string of the format <slot>:<index> that uniquely identifies the segment pertaining to this notification.

tptThresholdNotifyZonePair.description: A string of the format <in zone UUID>:<out zone UUID> that identifies the zone pertaining to this notification.

tptThresholdFilterNotify.name: tptThresholdFilterNotify
tptThresholdFilterNotify.description: Notification: Used to inform the management station that a threshold filter threshold crossing has been logged.
